Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:30.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你要睡到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚才睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:35.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你忙什么啊忙到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我制作了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:43.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,该说厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我睡会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快起床…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:57.36,FBT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\pos(960,720)}通向黎明的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是谁害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去买个午饭连人影都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得买了面包再回教室太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得屋顶才更远…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 从哪看不都是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想她拿着便当去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,纱绘你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢 那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:35.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 公园的附近有艘很大船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的港口每次都会有别样的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是个拍照的好地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个马上就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那条河边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,登上大桥旁的台阶 就能把整个城市一览无余了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天放晴的时候那儿的景色真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:01.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天探望姐姐的时候 你能先去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,送去修的照相机修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得去店里拿才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事什么时候去不都行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 邂逅不知道在何时何地就会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指和天空的邂逅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有其他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉真名 办完事后我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又这么说 上次不也没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:38.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一点也没改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说真名被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空什么的 我最～讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没…嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:13.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫君被真名告白后一定觉得很不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以午休以后就翘课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:20.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 行了 虽然不知道你又在妄想什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近你们2个在一起的时间变多了这是个不争的事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,连塔子也是 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是去同一家医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,经常在一起也无可厚非嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去医院了 先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再试一次比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫君很喜欢天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:50.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起草莓样式的 星星和云样式效果会更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 又说这些莫名其妙的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她没弄明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,纱绘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的给我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 让我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都怪纱绘要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:50.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我这就把小依带回病房去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想他一会就来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.49,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃鱼子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是个难题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 看来没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 抱歉 我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然没发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,探病时间早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 明天一定要好好和苍乃道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真难办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:46.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 从哪开始找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明把钱放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,红色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你一头钻进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点红肿已经很庆幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过想吃鱼子酱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼子酱 鲑鱼子不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,吃倒是吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是想吃鹅肝酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鹅肝酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去买
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 公主很不高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是长途旅行有点累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找个地方藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天你来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了鹅肝酱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的那份都拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明天是苍乃的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:09.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带个到医院去 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话姐姐会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那么接下来我们去商店选购吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来？ 不是明天去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 必须得事先预订才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:29.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定要预订的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会说今天也有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我一定会去医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:46.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我要利用之前的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等 真名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:55.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近生日蛋糕的种类很多我们得多花点时间认真选
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会买一整块的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生日蛋糕嘛 这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,或许选个小点的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再小的话就只能插几根蜡烛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备插几根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃姐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:47.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:49.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:55.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依在自己生日前一天总是紧张的睡不着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依是不是有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我深信那样才算是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你要到什么时候才能叫对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直适应不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 昨天…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 虽然有点那个 今天特地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给 是双胞胎人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,二人眨眼的地方很吸引人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:51.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:52.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是姐姐的生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备了秘密的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:05.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的「没问题」啦「当然」啦这些完全没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.55,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天不就是说谎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.30,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,下次绝对不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.10,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,尽说谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天真是值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃也说说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这和姐姐没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,上次也是明明是上课却不在教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在屋顶上拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:32.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看来小依不是站在我这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小依要站在你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是依人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不讨厌依人拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:53.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 下次我把照片也带来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样的话 最好是黎明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为了姐姐我会鼓足干劲带一张很美的照片来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的人偶看起来姐姐好象也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看看其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为还有不少的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给我这个谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住所是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？住所？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 住所就写教会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好～吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 味道好象有点不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 之后去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,能赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才这么早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:19.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:23.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,----IM----
